Product Description

Tactical Smart Watches For Men Sport Watches For Men (answer/make Call), IP68 Waterproof Smart Watch With Heart Rate Blood Pressure Spo2 Sleep Tracker

Features:

1. Full Touch Fitness Watch: Stylish and Simple Appearance, 2.06" HD AMOLED Full Touch Screen. Easy Control with the Sensitive Touch Screen. Watch screen will light up every time you raise your hand.

2. Bluetooth Call Smartwatch: You can directly use this watch to answer make calls/play music/read messages/store contacts/view call history.

3. Music Playback and Control: You can carry music directly through the watch.

4. Pedometer Step Tracker Watch: Track your steps, calories burned, distance, pace, heart rate change, duration of movement.

5. 120+ Modes Activity Tracker: Support 120+ Multi-Sport Modes (walking, running, cycling, Basketball,et.)

6. Heart Rate/Blood Oxygen Monitor Watch: 24 hours continuous monitoring.

7. Sleep Monitor Watch: Automatically monitor and analyze sleep quality during night.

8. Smart Watch with Notifications: Receive Call / SMS Notification from Facebook, Twitter, Whatsapp,LinkedIn, Instagram etc.(Can not reply it)

9.IP68 Water Resistant : IP68 waterproof, which has a good waterproof effect for daily life, such as: washing hands, anti-sweat, anti-rain, etc.

10. Breathe Training: Relax yourself and have a break when you feel nervous or pressure.

11. Sedentary Alert: Vibrate to remind you while you having a long time working.

12. Alarm: Can set up to multiple Alarm Clocks.

Bluetooth smart watch with text and call

  1. With this bluetooth call watch, you don't miss any important calls,by using clear waterproof speakers. You can make, answer and refuse a call on your wrist, also receive message/app notification(including SMS,Whatsapp, Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Facebook messaging, LinkedIn, and more). Never miss a call and a message. In addition, you can also listen to music directly through the smart watch, get lost in the music, enjoy a colorful and intelligent life.
  2. With all notifications displayed on your wrist and alerted by vibration, you can keep your phone in your pocket without missing any important calls or messages when you're out walking, exercising, or seeing friends.

Fitness watch for men with 120+ Sport Modes

  1. This fitness tracker watch automatically and accurately track count your full-day steps, calories burned, distances, miles walked and duration to get a clear situation of your daily exercise.
  2. The square watches for men has 120+ sports modes to meet your various sports styles. You can choose the corresponding mode according to your sports (Walk,Run,Cycling,on foot,Rope Skipping,Work out etc.)
  3. After exercise, check the data on the exercise watch or related app (exercising time, average heart rate, distance, steps, calories).You can make better adjustments by analyzing these data.And exercise your sports data through the exercise tracker watch to arrange fitness plan.

Smart Watch with Heart Rate Monitor

  • This smart watch equipped with the advanced self-developed optical sensor and a powerful sensor engine, the accuracy of data monitoring has been effectively improved by 23%.
  • Our smartwatch real-time track your heart rate, blood oxygen, and sleep, pays attention to your health at all times, records physical changes, and helps you better understand your health.
  • You can also view recent data changes in the APP, as well as professional advice on your health status.Master the first-hand dynamics of heart rate, blood oxygen, to realize all-around health protection.

Sleep Tracker with Alarm Clock, bring you the healthiest way to wake up

  • Adopting advanced motion sensors, smart watch automatically monitor sleep status (deep sleep, light sleep and wake up time, and provide a comprehensive sleep quality analysis to help you adjust your sleep habits.
  • This classic digital watch can wake you up with alarm clock, you can set up to alarms in our app.

2.06" HD AMOLED Screen ＆ Customizable

  1. Change the dial as you like. 100+ Watch Faces to choose and upload your own picture.
  2. 2.06" inch full touch screen. Watch face will light up automatically when you lift and twist your wrist.
  3. Easier to read with five levels of brightness options in the sun or dark.
  4. Smart watch come with 2 watch bands of different colors

IP68 Waterproof Smart Watch

This smart watch is IP68 waterproof , which can prevent the sport watch against sweat, rain, and othelwater splashes, and help you to fully enjoy your exercise in all weather.

Fitness watch with stopwatch and Countdown

This Smartwatch has Countdown 、stopwatch and timer function.Activate the stopwatch function on the screen and record the exercise time. You can also use it to calculate more things.

Smart watch with camera control

Just open the App on your smartphone and find the shake camera function to take a photo by shaking your smart watch fitness activity.

How to connect the smart watch?

A: First of all, please be sure to connect our smart watch through the "FitCloudPro" APP.

1. Tum on the "Bluetooth" function of your phone.

2. Open the "Google Play" or the “APP Store".

3. Search for "FitCloudPro" APP and download it.

4. Open the APP, click "Please connect device", click "Select device",find “P110" and bind it.

B: Perform the following steps to enable the answer/call function.

1. After selecting "P110"to connect, on the mobile phone system pop-up pairing request, select pairing.

2. Tum on the call Bluetooth switch on the watch (used whent he watch cannot make calls and play media sound).

3. In the phone settings, in the system bluetooth, turn on these permissions of the P110.

4.Once connected, you could use the watch to answer/make calls anytime.

If you don't need to use the call function, you can turn off the answer/call function so that the battery can last longer.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    • Juan Peñuela
      5.0 out of 5 stars A Durable and Versatile Smartwatch for Everyday Use
      Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2025
      Color: BlackVerified Purchase
      The first thing that caught my attention about this smartwatch is its durability (IP68), making it perfect for daily use, whether I’m washing my hands or out in the rain. The battery is also a strong point, lasting between 4 and 5 days with normal use, including health monitoring, notifications, and some exercise. Additionally, the heart rate, blood oxygen, and sleep sensors work consistently, giving me a general overview of my physical condition.

      As for the design, the 2.06-inch AMOLED screen is clear and customizable, and the watch comes with two straps to mix and match. The sports features are comprehensive, with over 120 modes available; although I’ve only used walking and running, the step, calorie, and distance metrics seem fairly reliable. I can also take calls directly from my wrist, which is practical. Overall, it’s a well-balanced smartwatch for those seeking convenience and solid performance.
